images.description: Lush green tea fields roll over hills under a sunlight-dappled tree in Boseong, Korea.
Two taekwondo athletes in mid-fight; one is executing a high kick to the head of the opponent.
An illuminated neoclassical rotunda by a calm reflecting pool during twilight.
View from a shaded arcade showing a detailed historic building framed by archways against a blue sky.
A large crystal ball stands in a lush garden with flowers and a rustic wooden fence in the background.
An elderly man stands at a podium labeled 'Agricultural Science and Technology,' giving a speech.
Celebrity chef cooking in an outdoor kitchen surrounded by an audience, with a woman assisting him.
A plate of Thai yam mu yo salad with sliced sausage, onions, and herbs on a wooden table.
Underwater photo of a black smoker, a type of hydrothermal vent, emitting a plume of mineral-rich water.
A colorful street fruit market with bananas, mangoes, oranges, and other fruits on display.
A display of various vegan dishes, all labeled, under bright lights at a food counter.
An astronaut examines a large lunar rock on the moon's surface, with the desolate lunar landscape in the background.
Ancient Roman baths with columns and statues, a green pool, surrounded by classical architecture.
Two musicians are performing on stage, one singing into a microphone and the other playing guitar, with colorful stage lighting.
A colorful assortment of fresh fruits including apples, grapes, pears, nuts, lemons, and an orange pumpkin.
A singer performs on stage in a black skirt, jacket, and thigh-high stockings, holding a microphone.
A panoramic night view of lit-up Las Vegas hotels and a casino fronting a reflective water body.
A row of rental bikes lined up on a city street with buildings and clear skies in the background.
A dentist and assistant are performing a procedure on a patient in a dental clinic.
A scientist in a lab coat and hairnet is using a pipette and lab equipment near a window.
A P-51 Mustang aircraft in flight, captured from above with a landscape of water and land below.
Aerial shot of a city with dense housing, a large park, and a red bridge spanning a blue bay.
Several medical ampoules of different sizes and colors arranged on a white surface.
A group of skydivers in colorful gear is about to jump from an open cargo bay of a flying airplane.
An expansive warehouse with numerous workers at stations and aisles filled with packages and goods.
A French Bulldog dressed in a pink yoga outfit with a mat rolled up on its back, looking at the camera.
A man in a red shirt and helmet is joyfully zip-lining against a backdrop of trees and sky.
A giant panda is sitting and happily munching on bamboo leaves.
A woman is performing a yoga pose, 'Bhekasana,' lying on her stomach, bending her knees, and reaching back to touch her feet.
A man with curly hair, wearing a microphone headset, smiles and looks to the side against a blurred background.
A bottle of milk, a bowl of soybeans, and green pods on a wooden table, likely soy milk and its ingredients.
A dish of stir-fried green leafy vegetables with red chili peppers served on a white plate.
A woman is standing by a brick wall, wearing a cropped cable knit sweater, beige blazer, and blue jeans, gazing upwards.
A close-up of a baked acorn squash filled with a creamy soup, topped with herbs and breadcrumbs.
A shirtless man with a beard, wearing white pants, stands by a window holding a coffee cup, in a bright room.
A woman in a casual outfit with a black cap, graphic tee, and light blue jeans walks on a city street.
An opulent shopping arcade with a glass ceiling, luxury storefronts, and ornate lamps, likely in a high-end casino.
A delivery person in a pink jacket and helmet rides a bike with a large pink food delivery backpack.
Ingredients and a cookbook on a kitchen counter, suggesting preparation for baking.
A bunch of fresh red radishes with green leaves and white roots.
Two runners, a man and a woman, are smiling and jogging in a race, wearing numbered bibs and athletic gear.
An optometrist is examining a patient's eyes using a slit lamp in a clinic.
Two models in stylish black and white attire holding hands, with a backdrop of cacti and a water body.
A woman performs on stage wearing a sparkling, jeweled black bodysuit, with her hair in motion.
